did.head: DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY
did.unittitle: Heterosexual and miscellaneous pornography periodicals, circa 1950-2003
did.repository: Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library
did.abstract: Small runs of erotic magazines aimed mostly at a heterosexual male audience. Models are mostly female. Titles may be published in the United States or internationally.

scopecontent.head: COLLECTION DESCRIPTION
scopecontent.p: Small runs of erotic magazines aimed mostly at a heterosexual male audience. Models are mostly female. Titles may be published in the United States or internationally.

prefercite.head: Cite As:
prefercite.p: Heterosexual and miscellaneous pornography periodicals, #7739. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.

relatedmaterial.head: RELATED MATERIALS
relatedmaterial.p: All the individual titles that comprise this collection are included in the bibliographies of U.S. and international periodicals in the Human Sexuality Collection, available at http://rmc.library.cornell.edu/HSC/per.htm instead of a call number, the collection number 7739 is listed.
Related collection: Male Model Pornography Magazine Single Issues, #7633.
Related collection: Miscellaneous Human Sexuality Periodicals, #7687.
